# Minimal Installation Policy
# Ensures core components are present

# Core packages
MUST package_installed base "Base system must be installed"
MUST package_installed linux "Linux kernel must be installed"
MUST package_installed networkmanager "NetworkManager must be installed"

# Desktop requirements
MUST package_installed hyprland "Hyprland compositor must be installed"
MUST package_installed kitty "Terminal emulator must be installed"
MUST package_installed firefox "Web browser must be installed"

# Services
MUST service_enabled NetworkManager "NetworkManager must be enabled"
SHOULD service_enabled sddm "SDDM display manager should be enabled"
